These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peach, plum, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, puzzles, writing
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, blood-red, azure, mauve
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, begonia, marigold, poppy
There are 4 different nationalities: french, chinese, british, polish
 1. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the person who growsorchid##1
 3. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person who likes azure is between the french and the person who growspoppy##2
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the polish##1
 9. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
10. the french is between the person who likes azure and the person eating radish##2
11. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the chinese##1
12. the person who likes mauve is the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the person who growsmarigold is between the person who growsbegonia and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea        | coffee       | lemonade  | almond-milk |
| Food          | radish     | plum         | peach     | broccoli    |
| Hobby         | gardening  | fishing      | puzzles   | writing     |
| Color           | blood-red | aquamarine | azure   | mauve     |
| Flower   | begonia    | marigold         | orchid | poppy         |
| Nationality         | polish     | french     | chinese  | british       |

