.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, surfing, sailing, basketball
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, skydiving, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, folk, gospel
4 different games are played: whist, canasta, monopoly, billiard
House: modern, farmhouse, gothic-revival, cottage
 1. the person playing canasta is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the modern house##2
 2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 4. the person playing canasta is between the person who's sport is swimming and the gothic-revival house##2
 5. the fan of disco is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the gothic-revival house is between the person watching action movies and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
11. the fan of disco is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
13. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
14. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Sport      | basketball    | surfing       | sailing   | swimming |
| Hobby         | chess     | skydiving   | writing    | filmmaking  |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel | thriller   | western     |
